description: Tucked away on a private, tree-lined street in Beverly Hills Post Office, this impeccably renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of modern indulgence and natural tranquility. The expansive open living space is bathed in natural light, while the updated kitchen features stainless steel appliances and stylish finishes. A secluded second-floor primary bedroom with a spacious private balcony, ideal for soaking up the sun in serene solitude. A stunning rooftop deck provides sweeping views, ideal for both entertaining and relaxation. Surrounded by lush greenery, the home offers ultimate privacy yet is just moments from Beverly Hills' most exclusive destinations. Enjoy the outdoors with nearby Coldwater Canyon Park and Franklin Canyon Reservoir offering scenic hiking trails, relaxing afternoons in the park, and serene reservoir views. This property presents a rare opportunity to live in one of the most coveted zip codes in the world.
